PackageName: spi-driver
SPDXID: SPDXRef-Package-spi-driver
PackageVersion: 1.1.0
PackageSupplier: Organization: asiball ()
PackageDownloadLocation: git+https://github.com/asiball/private-test-cpp-project.git#driver
FilesAnalyzed: false
PackageLicenseConcluded: MIT
PackageLicenseDeclared: MIT
PackageCopyrightText: Copyright (c) 2024 asiball
PackageComment: Linux SPI device driver static library (libspi_driver.a). Includes SpiDriver (spidev ioctl interface) and KernelSpiDriver (custom kernel module ioctl interface). Uses syslog for logging, fcntl/unistd for device file access.

PackageName: my-spi-driver
SPDXID: SPDXRef-Package-my-spi-driver
PackageVersion: 1.1.0
PackageSupplier: Organization: asiball ()
PackageDownloadLocation: git+https://github.com/asiball/private-test-cpp-project.git#kernel
FilesAnalyzed: false
PackageLicenseConcluded: GPL-2.0-only
PackageLicenseDeclared: GPL-2.0-only
PackageCopyrightText: Copyright (c) 2024 asiball
PackageComment: Linux kernel SPI device driver module (my_spi_driver.ko). Registers with Linux SPI subsystem via probe(), exposes /dev/my_spi_dev character device, controlled via MY_SPI_IOC_CONFIG/MY_SPI_IOC_TRANSFER ioctl. Requires running Linux kernel with SPI subsystem enabled.

