PackageName: glibc
SPDXID: SPDXRef-Package-glibc
PackageVersion: NOASSERTION
PackageSupplier: Organization: Free Software Foundation ()
PackageDownloadLocation: NOASSERTION
FilesAnalyzed: false
PackageLicenseConcluded: LGPL-2.1-or-later
PackageLicenseDeclared: LGPL-2.1-or-later
PackageCopyrightText: NOASSERTION
PackageComment: GNU C Library. Provides POSIX interfaces used across driver and library components: pthread (thread management in libdevice), syslog.h (logger.hpp in driver), fcntl.h/unistd.h (file operations in spi_driver.cpp and kernel_spi_driver.cpp), sys/ioctl.h (ioctl calls in both drivers).

PackageName: linux-kernel-headers
SPDXID: SPDXRef-Package-linux-kernel-headers
PackageVersion: NOASSERTION
PackageSupplier: Organization: Linux Kernel Organization ()
PackageDownloadLocation: NOASSERTION
FilesAnalyzed: false
PackageLicenseConcluded: GPL-2.0-only WITH Linux-syscall-note
PackageLicenseDeclared: GPL-2.0-only WITH Linux-syscall-note
PackageCopyrightText: NOASSERTION
PackageComment: Linux kernel headers. Userspace UAPI (Linux-syscall-note exception applies): linux/spi/spidev.h (SpiDriver), linux/ioctl.h and linux/types.h (my_spi_dev.h shared ioctl definitions). Kernel module internal headers: linux/spi/spi.h, linux/module.h, linux/miscdevice.h, linux/uaccess.h, linux/slab.h, linux/mutex.h (my_spi_driver.c). Build-time only for userspace; kernel module compiled against the running kernel's build tree.

